{"tid":1920841,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"消防處控制組同事強調絕對唔會事先假設市民“濫用”，所有個案都派員到現場處理同了解","createTime":"2020-03-11T17:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T17:17:43.000Z","uid":105567,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9961a10c42199b9477917fa6a4a6dd71bd603ffd","tid":1920841,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lw2J1iY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLw2J1iY.jpg&h=0818773c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aca606a50487529c231212aef568de7f11a98b0d","tid":1920841,"uid":105567,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:08:26.000Z","msg":"《服務承諾》<br />\n<br />\n消防處控制中心於日前凌晨青衣回收場大火中，由於濃烈嘅「燒膠味」飄往香港九龍大部份地區，於3小時內共接獲多達50宗以上嘅火警求助個案電話， <strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">控制組同事強調絕對唔會事先假設市民&ldquo;濫用&rdquo;，所有個案都派員到現場處理同了解，亦盡全力趕及5分鐘內到場嘅服務承諾</span></span></ins></strong>。<br />\n就算去到現場證實冇煙冇火， 同事都只會認為市民係「善意」虛報，而非惡意癱瘓消防處。感謝全香港嘅兄弟們由凌晨兩點忙到天光，為嘅只係確保每一位香港市民(不論你係黑衣人、白衣人定係睡衣人)嘅人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n東網新聞傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200310/mobile/bkn-20200310023355715-0310_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200310%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200310023355715-0310_00822_001.html&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=5059317d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200310/mobile/bkn-20200310023355715-0310_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n#服務承諾就係服務承諾<br />\n#無藉口 #消防控制中心<br />\n#新消聯 #HKFAC"},{"pid":"4a5bf7eca29bb27460b1c70f1bdaf65085a36e35","tid":1920841,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d28f719d7516198c35e5b0cf01dce760cfa0e0","tid":1920841,"uid":147226,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:11:09.000Z","msg":"連政府啲 pr 都食咗誠實豆沙包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104112821058132/posts/154341162701964/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104112821058132%2Fposts%2F154341162701964%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=ce2f3d98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104112821058132/posts/154341162701964/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消防員不停接到求助電話，縱使知道氣味源頭是青衣的一場火災，然後消防員仍然選擇在各區奔波，接聽市民的電話求助<span style=\"color: red;\">，並沒有像警察般接到市民求助時掛斷電話，甚至把警局關門。</span>"},{"pid":"3551a7e3cd092c14ba4d39dac0f46dc21b1fbe64","tid":1920841,"uid":108386,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:11:23.000Z","msg":"串到應一應"},{"pid":"5c243ddd0d4c94aa706dd4acfe50166676ac41b6","tid":1920841,"uid":52276,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"警犬就威呢，未接聽/唔接聽電話都已經知係元朗白衫人打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就照count做同一件案件。因為佢地有份一齊策劃嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294b054ebbdcc00f01ee5fd858691c742581f813","tid":1920841,"uid":150036,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係正常嘅紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e65f7d37b0d6afab23706d6e20f8b3e4519ea67","tid":1920841,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"294b054ebbdcc00f01ee5fd858691c742581f813","tid":1920841,"uid":150036,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係正常嘅紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"所以點解我地咁鍾意消防<br />\n佢哋起碼正常"},{"pid":"896b45d0c6dded0719a2003bf